rows.label: tlk41100171_03_msg0001
rows.name:
There're tourists who toss coins over
the edge at Milama Viewpoint, but a lot
of them actually land around here.

rows.label: tlk41100171_03_msg0002
rows.name:
Though actually, I haven't seen that
many coming down lately. I guess
people lost interest?

rows.label: tlk41100171_03_msg0003
rows.name:
Well, I've almost earned enough to go
home to Gula anyway. I'm thinking
of taking my dad along with me...
